Adjusts the available modeline horizontal resolution
to match the game image\(cqs size. The stretched modeline
keeps all the clock attributes of the original
modeline. Also all other modeline attributes,
like doublescan and interlace, are maintained.
.HP 4
.I clock
Adjusts the available modeline\(cqs vertical clock
to match the game\(cqs frame rate.
.HP 4
.I xclock
Adjusts the available modeline\(cqs horizontal resolution
and the vertical clock.
.HP 4
.I generate_exact
Creates automatically some new modelines using
the format specified on the \(oqdevice_video_format\(cq
option. The generated modelines will be named \(oqgenerate\(hy*\(cq.
Check the \(oqadvdef.txt\(cq file for the description of
the \(oqdevice_video_format\(cq option or simply use the
\(oqadvcfg\(cq utility to set it up correctly.
If the \(oqdevice_video_format\(cq option isn\(cqt
