.PP
The \(oqgenerate\(cq options are able to create at runtime all the
required modelines. You don\(cqt need to create a list of modelines
manually.
.PP
The not \(oqgenerate\(cq options use only the modelines defined with
the \(oqdevice_video_modeline\(cq option in the configuration file.
You can add them manually or using the \(oqadvv\(cq utility.
Check the \(oqadvdev.txt\(cq file for more details on the
\(oqdevice_video_modeline\(cq option.
